    "description": "<strong>“火山方七百里，高万仞，愚公常思火山之炽烈，扰民百姓，遂立志灭之！”</strong><br>于是，上天感动于愚公的虔诚，决定派你去帮助愚公灭火山。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>火山</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/77c682720841f69d6e60a813155caea2.avif?t=1735914436\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br>火山的心情明灭不定，每隔一段时间就会喷发，一旦喷发，愚公涂炭，请帮帮愚公们<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/8e1ef111d62ea6b148f9c8e6de813efa.poster.avif?t=1735914436\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/8e1ef111d62ea6b148f9c8e6de813efa.webm?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/8e1ef111d62ea6b148f9c8e6de813efa.mp4?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>哪该怎么办呢</strong></h2>欸！恰巧你是掌管鼠标点击和卡片造愚公的神！请通过鼠标神力和甚于粘土神力的卡片帮助愚公们吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/1617fe6ecbe93e491a8febd1cf780976.poster.avif?t=1735914436\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/1617fe6ecbe93e491a8febd1cf780976.webm?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/1617fe6ecbe93e491a8febd1cf780976.mp4?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>有策略的放置游戏</strong></h2>而在这期间，上天也会助你一臂之力，扑灭每轮蓄势待发的火势后，你将<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 获得新卡片之力<br></li><li> 领悟新的管理策略来管理愚公们</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/b38085f5d0900534f16f9abf15454235.poster.avif?t=1735914436\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/b38085f5d0900534f16f9abf15454235.webm?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/b38085f5d0900534f16f9abf15454235.mp4?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏内容</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 10-20小时游玩<br></li><li> 50+卡牌</li></ul><strong>如果你喜欢在游戏中探索各种流派和打法，这游戏绝对适合你。</strong><br><br>欢迎加入官方QQ群：991985688",
